title: We Made Our Own High Fashion Runway Show - H3 Podcast #237
description:
On this episode of the H3 Podcast IT'S FASHION WEEK... or day, or whatever. Ian takes us on a journey through the world of high fashion concept pieces, and the crew goes ahead and presents their own high fashion pitch for Teddy Fresh!
